408
00:19:55,087 --> 00:19:56,964
What is this place?

409
00:19:58,883 --> 00:19:59,842
Philippe, please!

410
00:19:59,883 --> 00:20:00,884
Steady!

411
00:20:02,469 --> 00:20:03,679
Steady.

412
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,850
Papa.

