414
00:20:11,686 --> 00:20:13,896
Just had to invite him
to stay, didn't we?

415
00:20:13,938 --> 00:20:15,398
Serve him tea.

416
00:20:15,439 --> 00:20:16,941
Sit in the master's chair.

417
00:20:16,982 --> 00:20:18,275
Pet the pooch.

418
00:20:18,317 --> 00:20:20,110
l was trying
to be hospitable.

419
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:22,613
Hello?

420
00:20:22,654 --> 00:20:25,365
ls anyone here?

421
00:20:25,407 --> 00:20:28,910
