434
00:20:52,890 --> 00:20:53,975
Papa?

435
00:20:55,726 --> 00:20:56,602
Did you see that?

436
00:20:59,104 --> 00:21:00,397
lt's a girl!

437
00:21:00,439 --> 00:21:01,690
