00:21:11,574 --> 00:21:12,992
Papa?

444
00:21:14,243 --> 00:21:15,536
Papa?

445
00:21:17,329 --> 00:21:18,497
Hello?

446
00:21:18,539 --> 00:21:20,374
ls someone here?

447
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:21,667
Wait!

448
00:21:21,708 --> 00:21:23,627
l'm looking for my father. l...

449
00:21:26,004 --> 00:21:27,130
