to leave this place.

458
00:21:43,770 --> 00:21:44,813
Who's done this to you?

459
00:21:44,855 --> 00:21:46,148
No time to explain.

460
00:21:46,189 --> 00:21:47,148
You must go! Now!

461
00:21:47,190 --> 00:21:48,149
l won't leave you!

462
00:21:48,191 --> 00:21:49,651
What are you doing here?

463
00:21:49,692 --> 00:21:50,568
Run, Belle!

464
00:21:50,610 --> 00:21:52,153
Who's there?
Who are you?

465
00:21:52,153 --> 00:21:53,905
The master of this castle.

466
00:21:54,655 --> 00:21:56,324
l've come for my father.

467
00:21:56,365 --> 00:21:57,783
Please let him out.

468
00:21:57,783 --> 00:21:58,951
Can't you see he's sick?

469
00:21:58,993 --> 00:22:00,994
