trespassed here!

470
00:22:01,036 --> 00:22:02,579
But he could die.

471
00:22:02,621 --> 00:22:03,830
Please, l-l'll do anything.

472
00:22:03,872 --> 00:22:06,374
There's nothing you can do.

473
00:22:06,416 --> 00:22:07,459
He's my prisoner.

474
00:22:07,584 --> 00:22:09,919
Oh, there must be
some way l can...

475
00:22:09,961 --> 00:22:11,004
Wait!

476
00:22:16,384 --> 00:22:18,010
Take me instead.

477
00:22:18,093 --> 00:22:20,721
