Yes. But you must promise
to stay here forever.

484
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:37,236
Come into the light.

485
00:22:48,621 --> 00:22:49,664
No, Belle!

486
00:22:49,748 --> 00:22:52,750
l won't let you do this!

487
00:22:54,210 --> 00:22:55,294
You have my word.

488
00:22:55,336 --> 00:22:57,254
Done!

