Tale as old as time

1595
01:21:40,609 --> 01:21:43,779
Song as old as rhyme

1596
01:21:43,820 --> 01:21:50,243
Beauty and the Beast.

1597
01:22:04,631 --> 01:22:09,135
Ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh, ooh, ooh

1598
01:22:13,264 --> 01:22:19,311
Tale as old as time

1599
01:22:19,353 --> 01:22:24,733
True as it can be

1600
01:22:24,775 --> 01:22:28,278
Barely even friends

1601
01:22:28,278 --> 01:22:31,155
Then somebody bends

1602
01:22:31,197 --> 01:22:36,952
Unexpectedly

1603
01:22:36,994 --> 01:22:43,000
Just a little change

1604
01:22:43,041 --> 01:22:46,169
Small to say the least

1605
01:22:46,211 --> 01:22:49,088
Both a little scared

1606
01:22:49,088 --> 01:22:52,341
Neither one prepared

1607
